{"tid":304102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】反外判  壹傳媒工會宣布罷工15分鐘","createTime":"2017-06-30T15:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T16:33:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60ae5c5b619b715e37260796aa7fb13ad9aace5d","tid":304102,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"2008年，因應減薪，壹傳媒工會成立；這些年來，工會呼籲同事捍衛新聞自由、聲援被捕攝記、關心上庭手足，喊口號舉橫額、做雨傘撐佔領，大小社會事務，都有壹同事的身影；同一時間，我們卻忍痛看著同事一個接一個捧紙箱收行裝，無情被裁。到這一次，我們要為自己發聲，要離開工作崗位15分鐘抗議，在壹蘋果大樓外默站，向外判方案和無情裁員表達強烈憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n看似平靜時，工會仝人吃盤菜、切乳豬、抽機票，但我們清楚知道團聚的歡樂非常短暫，頸上的屠宰之刀其實從未離去，工會維護同事權益刻不容緩。現實卻是集團裁員連年，部門的空凳一張添一張，Canteen人潮買少見少，到我們終於習慣了這種朝不保夕的裁員日子，新一招又來了 ── 把員工外判出去。<br />\n如果我們是手足，外判行動就是斬去手腳，人心潰散、士氣低落，我們不禁問，這種狀態下，集團可以怎樣前行？今天先宰美術部，明天可以是任何人，唇亡齒寒，由壹集團、以致整個行業，都將發生巨變。<br />\n<br />\n工會連日來就外判計劃與管理層周旋，集團不單一意孤行，更同時開展零星裁員，兩名由創刊服務至今的《蘋果日報》財經組同事，昨日突然被通知其負責的版面被取消，二人即時被遣散，而且不獲任何額外補償，22年的僱傭關係一夜抹殺，工會對此感極度憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n僅離席15分鐘，有用嗎？可以改變甚麼嗎？這是記者掙扎求存的年代，這是傳媒走向零散化的開始，如果這也是壹傳媒做為良好僱主的句點，在這座大樓上班的每一個人，絕對有資格表態、發聲，在歷史這一筆留下足跡。因為默然無聲不是我們的Style，一如2014年佔領期間我們勇抗大媽，在傳媒腐朽變質的洪流底下，讓我們在同一地點再一次奮力抵擋。<br />\n<br />\n壹工會史無前例地，發動同事為自己的權益發聲，會有風險嗎？是的，每一步、每個行動都會有風險，以為如常工作執行指令就沒有風險嗎？被裁的員工曾經犯錯過甚麼嗎？難道我們該坐以待斃，繼續每天等候發落嗎？<br />\n<br />\n各位同事，每個人都要為自己的飯碗抗爭，今日不站出來，也不要期望有順風車；<br />\n仍然買報讀報的讀者們，我們今次需要你；在手機瀏覽的網友們，請伸出援手；<br />\n<br />\n一直在採訪路上與我們並肩的同業行家，請幫助我們；即將加入傳媒業的同學，為了自己和整個行業的發展，請和我們一起發聲。<br />\n<br />\n堆填區萬里路遙，但存亡之間，壹工會懇請同事、同業、學生、公眾，來將軍澳工業邨聲援我們，除了陪伴我們渡過這黑暗的15分鐘，也參與網上聯署 (<a href=\"http://goo.gl/9W21E1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9W21E1&d=iKyNaObySeIne9ooppA8fkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=94a95073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/9W21E1</a> ) ，做我們抗爭的後盾。<br />\n<br />\n工會屆時將向集團管理層重申以下訴求：<br />\n1. 立即撤回外判計劃<br />\n2. 停止黑箱談判，與美術部全體同事共同商討轉形方案及細節<br />\n3. 按年資為遣散同事提供額外補償<br />\n<br />\n行動安排：<br />\n日期：7月5日（星期三）<br />\n時間：傍晚6時正<br />\n地點：將軍澳駿盈街8號壹蘋果大樓C閘外<br />\n詳情：員工身穿黑衣，6時正集體離席到大樓C閘外默站15分鐘；誠邀公眾人士穿黑衣參與"},{"pid":"adc8b40886cccef8d6679c4aad08e0d0e4e8bf63","tid":304102,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f578bb7c5f0dec20210e2544bf242e2c34d50933","tid":304102,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"15分鐘"},{"pid":"28f7a1af1a1fd31c1dae697ce6bc10f4ce88f341","tid":304102,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"15分鐘"},{"pid":"53a980729a85e2d30586f28977f9f631c5355820","tid":304102,"uid":106797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"15分鐘 好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時D人去廁所蛇王都唔止啦"},{"pid":"ce41dc9b0f5a8cc1240455832616a609620a199c","tid":304102,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪當down server囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf2d734dce0c946a1bd4cf3ef0e8cc766289c8d","tid":304102,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c83a4adc3fb4f03aca10be76a41096ac3d83bc0f","tid":304102,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054c0365b5871c6253a3b8f1f257a926d4d57a50","tid":304102,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"6點收左工喇喎 點罷工？"},{"pid":"f1edd53fc0b4d35a7e2b81ad74238088e0fdaccb","tid":304102,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲就係香港人?"},{"pid":"6c2804ef0df680ceceb94f38720bc8967f7bf79d","tid":304102,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6點收左工喇喎 點罷工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收咗工再罷工15分鐘<br />\n點解我從來都冇諗過可以咁對付老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做傳媒嘅朋友思想果然前衛<br />\n肥佬黎呢鑊仲唔嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今個禮拜六日放假又霸吓工喺屋企抗議<br />\n等老細加我人工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c08670a77db8db807291a619e9197d2797e77b","tid":304102,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6點收左工喇喎 點罷工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收咗工再罷工15分鐘<br />\n點解我從來都冇諗過可以咁對付老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做傳媒嘅朋友思想果然前衛<br />\n肥佬黎呢鑊仲唔嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等我今個禮拜六日放假又<span style=\"color: red;\">罷</span>吓工喺屋企抗議<br />\n等老細加我人工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef33c320e066aba0fcb079eeaddabb71f8e62eb7","tid":304102,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"OK,15分鐘後見"},{"pid":"7f75a688211e6458166428692e38375035187600","tid":304102,"uid":46764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"柒撚過今天我"},{"pid":"879d8b9ce70d57a8f5ec9609a895c0b1dab37354","tid":304102,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6點收左工喇喎 點罷工？</blockquote><br />\n諗起之前好似有單新聞<br />\n啲員工話準時收工當抗議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2406ebe9df6561588c229f175830ba495833aaba","tid":304102,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"15日先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}